node.text:
Gossip Girl, 2021

I loved working with these women. Each one fiercely talented, confident, beautiful, and kind. Jordan brought the fire. A radiant energy and joy to play with. Whitney a piercing gaze and charm. Emily a deep soul and strong sense of self. All three incredible forces representing the next generation.
